lic Square<br />\n的士佬好難得識英文 嗲左幾句<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dzsUZog.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdzsUZog.png&h=90067562&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMonument of independence<br />\n另一邊封晒維修緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無癮 去食第一餐<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EGYQxKV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEGYQxKV.png&h=1f357227&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pRxUZpZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpRxUZpZ.png&h=1a46318f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aAjszYo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaAjszYo.png&h=ca1e7a47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xY4szZR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxY4szZR.png&h=1ef13fa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n環境唔錯 間野叫kishlak 中亞菜餐廳<br />\n碟馬肉我已經食左5、6舊先影相 好大碟<br />\n有脂坊既位好食好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n湯同飯都好味<br />\n但真係太多食淨好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da5476113f04a03248476651c284d3c573f0439f","tid":1061410,"uid":99381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c23210b2cdae2f0abcf743ae96070c5c64a2ff59","tid":1061410,"uid":122444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T12:17:19.000Z","msg":"土耳其里拉 有無得係香港找換店 兌定先?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T12:52:52.000Z","msg":"應該好少有 我去到先禁錢 周圍都有銀聯"},{"pid":"08052fa6cbf2fd2e23222ee416e680bfc878950f","tid":1061410,"uid":122444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da5476113f04a03248476651c284d3c573f0439f","tid":1061410,"uid":99381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c23210b2cdae2f0abcf743ae96070c5c64a2ff59","tid":1061410,"uid":122444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T12:17: